solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Align the agent on the vertical axis (x=19) by moving RIGHT and UP. Because the agent is at x=5, it must move RIGHT 19 - 5 = 14 times to reach the opening in the enclosure at (18, 8). Next, move DOWN to align with the goal object's y-axis (y=10). Because the agent will be at y=8 after moving right, it must move DOWN 10 - 8 = 2 times.
